Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.47,0:00:09.86,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,The intense battle has reached its endgame and Meng Ao has finally faced off against Lian Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.54,0:00:05.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）\N激烈なる戦いは 最終局面を迎え
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:09.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙驁(もうごう)は ついに廉頗(れんぱ)と相対した
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.85,0:00:15.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敗北を重ねた男への雪辱を\N果たすことはできるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.86,0:00:15.67,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,Will this man who has suffered numerous defeats finally have vindication?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:20.98,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:21.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信(しん)）いてっ…\N（尾平(びへい)）立てるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:22.15,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:24.51,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Just stop my leg from bleeding, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:26.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手当ては 脚の止血だけでいい\Nそれより 馬を持ってきてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.51,0:00:26.78,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Somebody, go bring a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.64,0:00:27.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平･慶(けい)）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:30.87,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Mr. Yuan, how is the enemy army looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:31.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）渕さん　敵軍の様子は？\N（渕）はい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.87,0:00:36.01,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. They've lost morale after having heard of Lun Hu's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:33.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（渕）輪虎(りんこ)討ち死にの報により
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.21,0:00:37.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勢いは失いましたが\N総崩れというわけでもありません
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.01,0:00:38.05,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,but they haven't been completely routed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.72,0:00:41.05,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,So they have the advantage?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:42.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,優勢ではあるんだな？\N（渕）今のところ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:42.55,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,As of now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.55,0:00:45.56,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mr. Yuan, could I leave this place to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.62,0:00:45.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渕さん 悪い　ここ任せていいか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.05,0:00:48.94,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Lord Xin, you don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:48.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信どの まさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:50.30,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:55.71,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I still have... one last place to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:55.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後に まだ行く所があるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.57,0:01:04.58,Kingdom - Episode Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fs80\be0.25\c&H000000&\pos(646.857,92.571)}Meng Ao, Standing Firm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:10.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵たち）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:21.76,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Stop them here at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:21.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（守備隊長）なんとしてでも\Nここで食い止めろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:26.89,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,If they get past here, they can make it \Nstraight up to the headquarters at the peak!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:26.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここを抜かれては もう\N頂上の本陣まで 一気に抜かれるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:37.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（守備兵たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:44.99,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Here they come! Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.88,0:01:44.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（守備兵）来るぞ 準備しろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.98,0:01:47.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（守備兵）廉頗だ！\N（守備兵）廉頗が来るぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:46.08,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It's Lian Po!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:47.62,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lian Po is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:51.81,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,So the moment has finally come, has it? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.68,0:01:51.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）いよいよ\N時がやって来たようじゃのぅ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:56.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしの40年の思いを\N存分に受け止めてもらうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:58.69,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,You're going to feel the brunt of 40 years of my emotions, Lian Po! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:01:58.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗よ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:03.03,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, in the central battle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:02.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）そのころ 中央の戦いでは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:07.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎の死により さしもの魏国(ぎこく)軍も\N勢いを失いつつあった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:07.74,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,the death of Lun Hu was causing even the State of Wei army to lose momentum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.14,0:02:13.40,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,Just one more push, Yufeng Unit!\NNow is the time to stand firm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:13.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（番陽(ばんよう)）あとひと息だ 玉鳳(ぎょくほう)隊！\N今が ふんばり時ぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.31,0:02:17.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（斬る音）\N（魏兵たち）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:19.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:26.28,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,You are concerned about the headquarters, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.42,0:02:26.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり\N本陣の様子が気になりますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.28,0:02:29.30,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,Lord Ben, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:29.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,賁(ほん)さま いかがなされます？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:32.97,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,It's fine. We'll fight here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:32.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁(おうほん)）\Nいい… 俺たちは ここで戦う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:37.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１兵たりとも魏国軍の兵を\N本陣の丘に登らせてはならない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:37.55,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,We must not let a single one of the State of Wei's soldiers climb the hill to our headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:41.23,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,That is the mission of the rear flying column, the Yufeng Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:41.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが\N後方遊撃隊たる玉鳳隊の使命だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:43.55,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,Brilliant resolve, Lord Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:43.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（番陽）見事な お覚悟です 賁さま
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:45.21,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,Let's go, Pan Yang!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:45.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行くぞ 番陽\N（番陽）ははっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:45.93,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:48.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁）ハアッ！\N（兵士たち）ヤッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:02.07,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,Please be all right, Grandpa. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:03:02.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬(もうてん)）\N無事でいてくれよ じいちゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:06.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:09.71,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:09.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）信！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:10.98,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Meng Tian!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.76,0:03:12.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙恬\N（蒙恬）お前も本陣に？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:12.45,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,You're going to the headquarters, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:16.89,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,I started up this way when I heard Lun Hu was killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:18.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎を討ち取ったと聞いたから\N上ってきたんだが… そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:23.42,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,I see. So you really took down Lun Hu with your own hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.81,0:03:22.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に\Nその手で 輪虎を討ち取ったんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:27.94,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Those wounds tell a tale of a fierce battle to the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:27.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その傷が\N死闘の激しさを物語っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:33.69,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,You may have rendered the greatest achievement in this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:29.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひょっとしたら―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:33.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が この戦いちばんの\N武功を上げたかもな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:37.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）昨日の\Nお前の作戦ありきって話だけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:37.72,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,It all started from the strategy you came up with yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:41.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 戦自体 負けちまったら\N全部がムダになっちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:41.86,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,But if we lose the war itself, it'll all be for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:44.36,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:44.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,急ごうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:48.45,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,To our general!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:49.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺らの大将の所へ\N（蒙恬）ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:49.46,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:07.71,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,The fact that they keep concentrating on me {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:07.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツらが わしらに\N集中し続けているということは―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:11.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中央軍が\N正面から迫れていないという証し
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:12.26,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,is a sign that the central army is not approaching from the front. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:16.17,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,Did something happen to Lun Hu? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:15.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎に何かあったか…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:25.03,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Oh no! Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:24.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭叫(かくきょう)）いかん！ く… 来るぞ！\N（廉頗）ウオーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:27.01,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Gather in front of Lian Po!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:28.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬令）殿の前を固めろ！\N（李充(りじゅう)）守備兵 急げ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:28.28,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Guards, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:30.03,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Hurry, that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:31.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（守備兵）急げ！ あっちだ！\N（朱可）殿の馬を引け！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:31.75,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Get the lord's horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:33.63,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,M-My lord, you must get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:33.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭叫）と… 殿 脱出を！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）要らぬ\N（郭叫）ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:34.94,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.03,0:04:39.79,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,I will not retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:39.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）わしは… ひかぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:55.68,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,Understood, my lord! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:55.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,承知いたしました 殿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:05:01.89,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Counter attack! Stop Lian Po no matter... no matter the cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:59.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,迎撃だ！ なんとしても…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:01.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんとしても廉頗を止めろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.98,0:05:07.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウワーッ！\N（郭叫）廉頗を止めろー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.19,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Stop Lian Po!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:08.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（守備兵）来た…\N（守備兵）来たぞ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:07.99,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:09.10,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:11.96,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Is the headquarters not fleeing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:13.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本陣は脱出しないのか？\N（守備兵）なに？ ホントか！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:14.15,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:14.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！ 来たぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:15.08,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:17.99,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Fire the arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:19.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,弓を射ろ！ 槍衾(やりぶすま)を作るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:19.83,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Create a line of spears!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:33.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ンーッ！\N（守備兵たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:36.10,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Use {\i1}it{\i0}{\alpha&HFF&}.{\alpha&H00&\4a&HA1&}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:35.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（守備隊長１）“あれ”を使うぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:40.90,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,B-But we only use it when those below have evacuated or been completely wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:40.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（守備兵）し… しかし“あれ”は\N下が撤退 もしくは全滅した際に…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:43.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やむをえん！\N（守備兵）それでは味方が…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.11,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,We have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.47,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Whose side are you on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:48.24,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Shut up! Our enemy... is Lian Po!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:45.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黙れ！ 敵は…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗なのだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:52.77,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,It's no good! We can't hold out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:52.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（守備兵）\Nダメだ！ 持ちこたえられない！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:55.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（守備隊長２）なんとしてでも\Nここで食い止めるぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:55.81,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,We must stop him here at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:02.00,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Wh-What?! Are they trying to kill their own allies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:06:01.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バ… バカな　味方を殺す気か！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:04.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（守備兵たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:08.34,Kingdom-Main,Aide,0,0,0,,That Meng Ao, it seems he's starting to panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:07.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（側近）\N蒙驁め 焦り始めたと見えまする
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フン…\N（側近）あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:12.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！ 将軍！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:13.01,Kingdom-Main,Aide,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:31.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハアッ！ ヤッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:40.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（守備兵たち）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:48.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（守備兵たち）\Nアアッ… ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:06.40,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,F-Finally... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:06.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（李充）つ… ついに…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:08.63,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,He's finally... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:08.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黄仁）ついに…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:11.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭叫）廉頗が来た！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:11.34,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,Lian Po is here! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:20.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前後から\N挟み込むつもりで攻撃してきたが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:20.71,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,I had intended for a pincer attack from the back and the front,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:24.24,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,but to think I was able to attack from just one side...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:24.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 片側だけで攻略できるとは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.44,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:26.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまらん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:31.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり\Nこんな戦では 燃え上がらんのぅ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:31.42,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Looks like this war won't make my blood boil after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:32.83,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It's Lian Po!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:34.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（朱可）廉頗だ！ 守備兵 取り囲め
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:34.58,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Guards, gather together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.02,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,K-Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:35.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こ… 殺せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:38.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（朱可）\Nと… 殿を！ 殿をお守りしろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:38.43,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Th-The lord! Protect the lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:41.93,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Don't get so flustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:41.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）そう取り乱すな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:50.69,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,The battle has only just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:50.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負は まだ これからじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:52.41,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,M-My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:53.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,と… 殿！\N（李充）一体 何を…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:53.69,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,What in the world are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:02.33,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,A-Are you intending to fight him one-on-one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:02.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭叫）ま… まさか 一騎打ちを？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:06.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬令）\Nと… 殿が廉頗と？ そんなムチャな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.86,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Y-You and Lian Po, my lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.86,0:08:06.41,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,It's too reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:15.47,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,It has been quite some time, Meng Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:15.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,随分と久しぶりじゃのぅ 蒙驁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:19.36,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,You haven't aged too gracefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:21.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,老け方が半端ではないわ\N（蒙驁）うるさいわい！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:21.19,Kingdom-Main,Meng,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:26.48,Kingdom-Main,Meng,0,0,0,,Lian Po, I'm delighted you remember me after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:26.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗よ まずは わしのことを\N覚えていたことをうれしく思う
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:29.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ… まあのぅ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:30.46,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:35.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの当時 わしが討ち取れなかった\N敵将は うぬくらいじゃったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:35.99,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,You were the only general from back then I wasn't able to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:41.74,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,That's because you turned tail the minute your outlook started to look bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:41.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何せ 旗色が悪くなると\Nすぐに逃げ出しおったからのぅ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:47.25,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,But just what is that skittish Meng Ao...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:46.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…で その逃げ腰蒙驁が―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:51.50,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,doing now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:51.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは 一体… 何のマネじゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:09:00.76,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Rather than dying an honorable defeat, wasn't shamefully running around relentlessly more your style?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:54.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,玉砕して散るより―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:09:00.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後まで情けなく逃げ回ったほうが\Nうぬらしかったのではないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:10.77,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,When you come to be our age, there are lots of things you may think even if you don't really like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:10.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お互い この年になると イヤでも\Nいろいろと思うところがあろうて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:19.38,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,And so, now that I've got this chance, I thought I'd like to talk to you a bit on horseback.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:15.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひいては この際 せっかくなので\N馬上で おぬしと―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:18.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,語らいたいと思うてのぅ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:28.54,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,You idiot. I have nothing to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.30,0:09:28.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このバカが… わしが\Nうぬと語ることなど何もないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:31.87,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Hey, don't say that, Lian Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:32.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ そう言うな 廉頗\N本当は おぬしも―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.87,0:09:36.00,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,I think you really want to talk with a certain someone, too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:37.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰かと語らいたいのではないのか？\Nフォフォフォフォ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:39.30,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:39.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なにぃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:09:58.94,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Is-Is it going to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:09:58.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は… 始まるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:10:03.28,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The lord and Lian Po... one-on-one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:10:03.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殿と… 廉頗の一騎打ちが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:08.65,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,Th-There really is no way the lord can win... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:08.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭叫）\Nと… 殿が勝てるはずがない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:15.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フン…\Nわしが誰かと語らいたいじゃと？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:15.81,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,I want to talk with someone, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:17.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,面白い
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:17.96,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:22.22,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Why don't I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.06,0:10:22.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういう意味か…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:35.02,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,have you tell me what you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:35.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,教えてもらおうではないか！\N（蒙驁）ンーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:50.65,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,L-Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:50.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,と… 殿！\N（兵士）アアッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:57.30,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,L-Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:58.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）殿！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:04.88,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,He managed to keep it shallow? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:04.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よけた分 浅かったか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:07.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）フォフォ…\N（兵士）無事だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:10.89,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,He's all right! The lord is all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:10.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）おお！ 殿！ ご無事だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:17.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フォフォフォフォ…\N相討ち覚悟の一撃 かわされたか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.18,0:11:18.67,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,My attack which I intended to perform while being hit myself still missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フォ… 惜しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:20.65,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,So close...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:24.28,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,You're such a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:24.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカが… そんなもの！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:31.66,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,It wasn't close at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:31.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひとつも惜しくないわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:35.80,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Meng Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:38.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）殿！ 蒙驁さま！\N（蒙驁）ウウッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:37.11,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Lord Meng Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:40.99,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,You're too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,弱すぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:47.06,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,What exactly did you think you could do with skill like that, Meng Ao?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:46.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな腕前で\N何かできると思ったか？ 蒙驁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:52.94,Kingdom - Episode Title,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\fs60\bord3\1a&HFF&\blur4\3c&HE1E2E2&\pos(458,109.333)}Meng Ao
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.52,0:11:52.94,Kingdom - Episode Title,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\fs60\bord0\be0.5\3c&HE1E2E2&\pos(458,109.333)}Meng Ao
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:13.45,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,It is not skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:14.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）腕前ではない\N（廉頗）うん？ オッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:17.66,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,My weapon right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:17.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の わしの武器は…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:21.21,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,is my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:21.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:30.98,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Lian Po, I am afraid of you to the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:30.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗よ\Nわしは 心底 おぬしが恐ろしい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:32.85,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,That is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:36.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃそうじゃ　若きころ\Nおぬしの前に 負けに負けを重ね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:36.54,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,When I was young, I lost to you again and again
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:39.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 一度も勝てなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:39.98,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,and in the end, I never had one victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:43.91,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,And when I heard that you were coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:43.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おぬしが出てくると聞いたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:48.74,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Honestly, that twist of fate made my vision hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:48.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正直 運命のいたずらに\N目の前が暗くなったわい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:53.16,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,I'm already at the age where I'm looking at retirement,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.27,0:12:53.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もはや\N引退の見えている この年になって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.14,0:12:57.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ\Nおぬしと戦うハメになるのかとのぅ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:57.61,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,why did I end up fighting you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:00.25,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.41,0:13:00.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃが そのとき
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:05.00,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,a young man said this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:04.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ある若者が\Nわしに こんなことを言ったのじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:11.04,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,"If I win in the end, I win it all."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:10.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後に勝ち逃げすれば\Nわしの総勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:17.64,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,And that I should be happy I've got a chance to make a comeback after all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:17.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この期に及んで一発大逆転の好機が\N巡ってきて良かったな …とな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:24.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フォフォフォフォ… なんとも愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:24.59,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,How happy that made me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:31.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,若さとは なんと まぶしき炎かな\Nその意見に わしも大賛成じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:28.30,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Youth really is quire a brilliant flame, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:31.41,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,I had to agree with that opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:34.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして今
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:39.59,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,And now, standing at the bottom line of my long military service with many ups and downs,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:39.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紆余曲折(うよきょくせつ)した我が戦歴の\N総決算の場に立ち
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:42.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふと こうも感じておる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:42.25,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,this is how I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:48.67,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,After abandoning my homeland, Qi, 40 years ago seeking success...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:48.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,40年前 祖国 斉(せい)を捨ててまで\N立身出世を求め
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:54.17,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,the fact that I was able to climb to the rank of Great General in the State of Qin...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:53.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秦国(しんこく)で\Nなんとか大将軍に上り詰めたのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:13:58.31,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,was all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:13:58.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:05.82,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,for this moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このときのためであったのだと！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:11.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:11.19,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウワッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:26.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ンンッ… こやつ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:26.84,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:34.35,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,How was that? An attack filled with 40 years' worth of fervent emotions?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:34.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうじゃ？\N40年の熱き思いの籠もった一撃は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:37.85,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Pretty heavy, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:37.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大層 重かろう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:42.60,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Lian Po. I do not think that inside of you right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:42.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗… 今の おぬしの中には―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:48.23,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,is something heated enough to defend against all of my intense emotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:48.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしの激情を受けきるほど\N熱きものは なかろうて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:50.89,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:50.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんじゃと！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:05.25,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Xin! If you're feeling weak, then rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:05.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信！\N苦しくなってきたんなら休んでいろ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:08.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘッ… 誰が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:08.00,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Who feels weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:17.32,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,There aren't any guards on the path\N to the headquarters at all. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:17.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし\N本陣までの道に 守備が全くいない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:22.45,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,Does that mean they were all brought around to the other side? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:22.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全て裏側に回っているということか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:25.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり 廉頗が…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:25.83,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,It's got to be Lian Po... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:28.49,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,Grandpa... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:28.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じいちゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:35.28,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,There it is, the headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:35.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）出たぞ 本陣！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:38.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッ… 誰もいねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:38.53,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Nobody's there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:52.30,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What the hell... happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:52.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一体 どうなって…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:54.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハアッ！\N（信）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:56.33,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Meng Tian!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:55.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙恬！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:57.51,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:57.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.76,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,A-Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:14.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）す… すごい\N（魏兵）あ… ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:14.15,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:19.11,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The one suffering wounds overwhelmingly is Lord Meng Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:18.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬公）傷を負わされているのは\N圧倒的に蒙驁さまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:25.29,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,But when he's getting hit by attacks, it's Lian Po that's being pushed back, horse and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:22.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 攻撃が当たれば必ず―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:25.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗を馬ごと吹き飛ばしている！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:30.04,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,They're heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:29.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,重いのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:34.42,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Even with his advanced age, the strength of his emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:34.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,身体 老いたりとも\Nこの“思いの強さ”とは…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:39.14,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,are delivering attacks with this much weight to them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:38.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これほど 一撃に重みを与えるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:42.68,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,No. I'm sure that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:42.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬令）\Nいや… きっと それだけではない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:45.62,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Perhaps since this is your first time seeing him fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:47.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦っているお姿を初めて見るせいで\Nみな肝心なことを忘れていないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:48.66,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,have you all forgotten something crucial?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:51.69,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Meng Ao is, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:51.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬令）蒙驁さまは もともと―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:57.37,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,the father of the State of Qin's general with unrivaled strength, General Meng Wu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:56.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秦国随一の怪力無双 蒙武(もうぶ)将軍の\Nお父上なのだぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:17:04.83,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It is not that strange to think that Lord Meng Ao could be superior to Lian Po in pure brute strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:17:01.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬令）\N蒙驁さまは単純に腕力だけなら―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:04.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗を上回っていたとしても\N不思議ではないのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:09.96,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Lian Po!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:10.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗さま！\N（魏兵）殿！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:10.58,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:15.51,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:15.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:20.39,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,General Meng Ao... is fighting one-on-one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:20.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙驁将軍が一騎打ちだなんて…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:26.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗！ おぬし自身\N本当は気づいておるのだろうが？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:26.60,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Lian Po. Have you really not realized it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.85,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,The golden age has ended!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:28.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黄金の時は去ったと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:33.15,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,When your greatest foes, the Six Great Generals passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:34.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最強の敵 六大将軍が去ったとき\Nおぬしの火も…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:37.11,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,your flame went out as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:37.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,消えたのじゃー！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:38.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:42.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！\N（魏兵）将軍！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:42.24,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:56.55,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Fall, Lian Po!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:54.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逝(い)けー！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:56.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:21.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じいちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:21.63,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,Grandpa... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:25.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙驁将軍…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:25.28,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,General... Meng Ao...  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:30.29,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,My arm... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:30.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腕が…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:41.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フン…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:47.93,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Meng Tian!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:47.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙恬！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:49.56,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Tian!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:49.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恬！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:54.31,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,R-Run, Tian!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.67,0:18:54.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,に… 逃げよ 恬！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:00.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:03.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部下たち）ウワッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:20.96,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,When the Six Great Generals passed\N away, my flame went out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:20.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）六大将軍が去りしとき\Nわしの火が消えたじゃと？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:23.09,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,You fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:22.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このバカが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:29.48,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Starting to proclaim triumphant things like that as if they're self-evident...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:29.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな分かりきったことを\N今更 得意げに ほざきおって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:36.24,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,And with my flame out, you're going to hit me with 40 years worth of emotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:36.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,火の消えた わしに うぬの\N40年の思いをぶつけるじゃと？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:41.47,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Did you think everything would work out for you, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:41.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなもので\Nどうにかなると思ったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:48.99,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,In that era, the State of Qin Six Great Generals and us State of Zhao Three Great Devas
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:48.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの時代 秦国六大将軍と\Nわしら趙国三大天(ちょうこく さんだいてん)は―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:53.71,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,grasped the flesh and blood of millions of soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:53.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,互いに数百万の兵の血肉を握りしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:59.88,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,and did nothing but devote ourselves completely to clashing them with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:59.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全身全霊を懸けて\Nそれをぶつけ合う戦いに明け暮れた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:07.76,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Even if some heat has been lost with such opponents gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:04.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その相手を失い
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:07.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,熱きものがなくなったとはいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:13.27,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,this adamantine body made and\N fought through that golden age!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:13.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの黄金の時代を\N戦い抜いた この金剛の体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:17.30,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,And you thought your mangy 40\N years of feelings or whatever
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:17.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うぬの\Nしみったれた40年の思いとやらで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:20.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吹き飛ばされるとでも思ったのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:20.27,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,could blow that all away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:25.03,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Do not make such light of me, Meng Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:24.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あまり わしらをナメるなよ 蒙驁！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:39.54,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Th-This is... Lian Po! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.87,0:20:39.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こ… これが廉頗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:58.91,Kingdom-Main,Bai,0,0,0,,Any new reports?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:21:00.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白亀西(はくきさい)）新たな報告は？\N（側近）まだ何も
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:21:00.31,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Nothing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:04.38,Kingdom-Main,Bai,0,0,0,,Send out messengers to gather information. Quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:03.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白亀西）伝者を出して\N情報を集めろ　今すぐにだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:06.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ははっ！ 伝者を呼べ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:06.43,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Call the messengers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:08.95,Kingdom-Thought,Bai,0,0,0,,This is General Lian Po. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:11.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白亀西）廉頗将軍のことだ\Nよもやということは あるまいが…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:11.58,Kingdom-Thought,Bai,0,0,0,,I am sure nothing could go wrong... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:15.28,Kingdom-Thought,Bai,0,0,0,,but I pray for his good fortune in battle. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:15.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ご武運をお祈りしておりますぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:35.46,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,So that's the headquarters of the Supreme Commander Bai Guixi, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:35.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（桓騎(かんき)）\Nあれが 総大将 白亀西の本陣か
